{
  "stem": "27507.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And because of that, we probably were able still to get some serum and so on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But there were doctors, yes, but as to the conditions in the hospitals in ghetto, I really don't know because I haven't ever been in.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But all of those things which belong to the community were usually unbelievably crowded, and un-- and there was hardly any money or equipment to keep you going.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I'm not sure how individual hospitals were existing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Ghetto was all together still an existing community, which was still living, in spite of terrible conditions.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Normal life was continuing in every aspect.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was, of course, government of the ghetto, which was the Judenrate.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was-- there were some kind of-- there was some kind of education.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was some kind of health service.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There was an-- there was a food supply, but food supply was, of course, something which was-- most of it was not official.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Most-- there was some official food supply because there were-- there were what was called kartki.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There were cards where you got some official rations.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There was official rationing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But official rationing was, I think, just enough to die of hunger.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That was, you got some bread and some artificial honey or artificial-- artificial jam and some other things, but never enough to keep you alive.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So the food supply was almost-- most of it was relying on smuggling contraband through the walls and through the gates of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And that was in different shapes that started with little children, children starting from a very early age probably up to the age of-- up to the teenagers, and, of course, grown-ups.",
      "word_count": 32
    }
  ],
